      "writtenOn": "2010-05-16T04:20:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "using empty lines in the text output for spacing purpose would be appreciated.\n\nIt would be nice if the documentation tried to explain what the option does. For example that this is really about connecting several emulators directly on a same emulated LAN (instead of having to go through two NAT proxies with redirections in the default case), that each emulator must have a distinct id/ip, or things will not work properly at all, etc...",
